---
alwaysApply: true
description: Folder structure for react project
---

Always use the following project structure:

```text
remotes/**/src/    
├── components/
├── hooks/
├── styles/
├── assets/
└── App.jsx
```

Rules:
- Reusable UI components → `components/`
- Custom React hooks → `hooks/`
- CSS/SCSS files → `styles/`
- Images, SVGs, fonts, and other static files → `assets/`
- Update `App.jsx` when integrating new components, routes, layouts, or providers.
- Do not create additional folders unless explicitly required.